OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy morning with the odd
OL,6,Fspot of light rain possible for
OL,7,FAberdeenshire, but predominately dry.
OL,8,FA dry afternoon with cloud breaking up
OL,9,Fto allow bright and sunny spells to
OL,10,Fbreak through. Light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FDry with some sunny spells at
OL,13,Ffirst but generally turning cloudier
OL,14,Fthrough the evening. Remaining largely
OL,15,Fdry and cloudy overnight with just a
OL,16,Ffew brief clearer intervals.
OL,17,
OL,18,CTuesday:FA dry and cloudy start, then
OL,19,Fcloud gradually breaking up through
OL,20,Fthe day to give some long sunny spells
OL,21,Fin the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
